bolism', 'Women using hormonal contraceptives should be advised of the risk of breakthrough bleeding and unintended pregnancy during concomitant rifamycin therapy, even when given in short courses.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/126542/', '', 'Estetrol', 'Capreomycin, Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Bedaquiline, Sulfamethoxazole, Streptomycin, Trimethoprim, Cycloserine, Isoniazid, Ethambutol, Pyridoxine, More', 1767369485);
